## Key Features
- ğŸš€ Automated Experimentation â€“ From hypothesis formulation, experiment implementation, experiment execution, result analysis and finding reflection.
- ğŸ“Š Rigor Enhancement - Built-in verification modules enforce methodical procedure, agent reliability and reproducibility.
- ğŸ”¬ Broad Applicability â€“ Supports [**ML Engineering**](https://www.just-curieous.com/machine-learning/research/2025-05-27-automl-co-scientist.html), [system analysis](./docs/example_logs/sorting_example/research_1748830453_20250602021413_iter1.md), and scientific discovery.
- ğŸ’» Use Your Starter Code â€“ Supports working on arbitrary user's starter code.
- ğŸ“‚ Bring Your Own Dataset â€“ Supports working on arbitrary user's datasets.
- ğŸ§¾ Automatic, Insightful Reporting - See a sample report [here](./benchmark/mle_bench/histopathologic-cancer-detection/histopathologic-cancer-detection_20250519225201_iter1.md)


